md:titleInfo.md:title: Arban jüg-ün ejen geser qayan-u tuyuji orusiba
Arban jüg-ün ejen geser qayan-u tuyuji orusiba

md:note.div:
Sanguozhi (三國志) oversat til mongolsk med titlen: Arban jüg-ün ejen geser qayan-u tuyuji orusiba (Historien om Geser-Khan, Herskeren over alle ti verdensretninger).
Oprindelig udarbejdet i årene 285-97 af Chen Shou.
Bloktryk i tværformat (55,5x17,5 cm) fra Beijing datered til Kangxi år 55 = 1716.
Katalogiseret i: Catalogue of Mongol Books, Manuscripts and Xylographs by Walter Heissig asssited by Charles Bawden. The Royal Library, Copenhagen 1971, s. 26-27
Mong. 469

Sanguozhi (三國志) translated to Mongolian with the title: Arban jüg-ün ejen geser qayan-u tuyuji orusiba (History of Geser-Khan, Lord of (all) ten directions).
Original comliled by Chen Shou in 285-97.
Peking xylograph (55,5x17,5 cm) dated to Kangxi 55 = 1716 CE.
Catalogued in: Catalogue of Mongol Books, Manuscripts and Xylographs by Walter Heissig asssited by Charles Bawden. The Royal Library, Copenhagen 1971, pp. 26-27
